What does strong and weak typing mean, and when would someone prefer a language that‚Äôs strongly/weakly typed?</p>

<h2 id="adding-colors">Adding colors:</h2>
<p>Cool repo to add colors to the command line output: https://github.com/fatih/color
run <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">go get github.com/fatih/color</code> in your project dir</p>
